---
title: Curried Chickpea & Butternut Squash Stew with Buttery Cilantro Pitas & Sour Cream
description: This hearty vegetarian chickpea stew tastes like it's been cooking for hours! You'll simmer butternut squash, chickpeas, and onion together in a curry-spiced broth. Serve over fluffy, fragrant basmati rice and finish with a dollop of sour cream and sprinkle of cilantro with buttery toasted pitas alongside.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/673b9282fd3e9058428acb88-ececcbbc.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/673b9282fd3e9058428acb88-en-US.pdf
nutrition:
